title: Just checking in
body:
Good morning Krista, 
 I hope you are well, 
 I just wanted to reach out to give you a quick update and also to thank you for last week, your help means more to me than you know. 
 I'm doing much better these days, I'm going out with friends like you suggested I do, and overall I'm okay. 
 Thank again and I'll see you soon, 
 Have a great day, 
 Elliot A.

title: Are we still on for tonight?
body:
Hi Trenton, 
 Please message me when you see this. 
 E.
